  "short_description": "Fly ship. Find way. Step outside. Make sense. Cloudome is a minimalistic game of flight, exploration, and puzzle solving with trace elements of mystery, laser shooting, and platforming. Prototype is its first version made in Unity, approximately half the size of the (hopefully) greater game to come.",
